OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 05 APR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1976FThe BBC English regions begin
OL,7,Fproviding local continuity during the
OL,8,Fevening on BBC One on a regular basis.
OL,9,FLocal continuity would be provided
OL,10,Ffive-days-a-week (Monday to Friday) and
OL,11,Fwould include a local news summary at
OL,12,Fclosedown.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1984FBBC One's schedule is cancelled
OL,15,Fdue to a strike by members of the
OL,16,FEntertainment Trades' Alliance over the
OL,17,Fsacking of 600 scenery shifters.
OL,18,FHowever, BBC Two's schedule is largely
OL,19,Funaffected, with the exception of
OL,20,FNewsnight.
OL,21,
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
